title: I Build an Industrial Empire on the Magic Continent
description: I Build an Industrial Empire on the Magic Continent Manhua [KK Original Submission Plan] Set in a medieval-style fantasy world, this world is filled with magic and adventure, where various races and cultures coexist. Noble estates, ancient castles, mysterious forests, and dangerous mountains make up the main scenes of this world. In this world, the protagonist is a young lord who inherits his family’s territory and wealth but faces various challenges and trials. Armed with the support of a system, the protagonist uses the industrial revolution to challenge the magical continent and ultimately dominate the entire land! 我在魔法大陆建立工业帝国 Forging an Industrial Empire in a Magical World I Dominate a Magical Continent with an Industrial Revolution
alternative_titles: 我在魔法大陆建立工业帝国
I Build an Industrial Empire on the Magic Continent
